Subject: Detection on Web upload
Description:
We are getting pop-up message of web upload blocked although there is nothing we are uploading in that website.

Kindly let us know what do on this and we want to schedule meeting as soon as possible.
What_We_Know__c: Fiel is blocked even if it does not contain the mentioned data.
Solution_Comment__c: Turned off Metadata Scanning to reduce uploads reports.
